<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1436,151,357]" pageId="8" pageNumber="483">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,1032,151,176]" pageId="8" pageNumber="483">Recorded damage and economic importance in the orchards of Iran:</emphasis>
