<bibRefCitation box="[510,652,188,213]" pageId="8" pageNumber="483" refId="ref21632" refString="Rajabi, Gh. (1991) Insects attacking Rosaceous fruit trees in Iran. Vol. 3: Homoptera. Ministry of Agriculture, Tehran, 256 pp." type="book">Rajabi 1991</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
